    "## Visual Example: Model Distribution Pie Chart\n",
    "\n",
    "This section visualizes the distribution of token usage across different models using a pie chart.\n"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 9,
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "data": {
